<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">śakābdam <num value="1361"><g type="numeral">1000</g> 3 <g type="numeral">100</g> 6 <g type="numeral">10</g> 1</num></hi>- ṉmel <hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> komāṟuvaṉmarāṉa <hi rend="grantha">tribhu</hi> vaṉacca<hi rend="grantha">kra</hi> vatti tirunelveliperumāḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>virapāṇṭiyatevaṟku yāṇṭu Iraṇṭā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>2- vatiṉ Etir patiṉeḻāvatu Āṭimātam <hi rend="grantha"><num value="31">3 <g type="numeral">10</g> 1</num> <g ref="sym:tam-pillaiyarCuli" type="punctuation"> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> </g></hi> tiruvaḻutivaḷanāṭṭu <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>vaikuntattu nāyiṉār kaḷḷappirāṉ koyilil tiruppati <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>vai<hi rend="grantha">ṣṇa</hi> var
<lb n="3" break="no"/><unclear>ka</unclear>ḷukku Iṉṉāyiṉārkku vaikācit tirunāḷ neṭunāḷāka naṭavāma<unclear>l</unclear> kiṭakkaiyil catai<unclear>ya</unclear>ttu nāḷ tuṭaṅki Eḻuntaruḷa Immātattil nammu
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṭaiya Āṭṭaip piṟanta nāḷ tiruvātiraiyile tirttam piṟacāta<unclear>ṅ</unclear>(k) kaṟpittu Itukku Ivvūr vaṭapiṭākaiyile Inta nāyiṉārkku muṉpu 
<lb n="5"/>viṭṭa tiruviṭaiyāṭṭamum U<hi rend="grantha">ṣā</hi>pūcaikku namperāl virapāṇṭiyaṉ cantiyāka nāḷ Oṉṟukku Amutupaṭi nāṉāḻiyāka naṭantupokak kaṟpittu Itukku cirākavaṉ<note n="318-1">This inscription stops here.</note>
</p>

